				<li id="16601959" class="cmnt-root" data="20" data-d="1649325607000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578404/Nightrider-Glaive" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">07 Apr 2022 06:00</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16601959" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">After 500 hours, this is my favorite weapon.  The running light attack comes out quickly and has excellent range for rollcatching when the opponent rolls straight away from you.  The running heavy is a broad sweep that is more applicable for when enemies try to roll behind you or to the side.  The standing light attack knocks jump spammers out of the air, and it also roll catches pretty well if you buffer your light attacks.  R1, walk forward a step, R1, walk forward a step, R1, etc.  Speaking of jump spam, the jumping attacks are also pretty nice.  This weapon takes many good ashes of war.  Flaming Strike is my favorite, but if you prefer to add ANOTHER rollcatch to your arsenal, try Giant Hunt or Sword Dance.  They are both excellent.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16601959" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16601959" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>20</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16601959"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16601959" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16601959"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
